Tidyverse core packages daily downloads

A dataset containing the daily downloads of tidyverse core packages from 2015-01-01 to 2016-12-31. The variables are as follows:

tidypkgs

Format

A data frame with 4386 rows and 3 variables:

date

Date when the downloads are made

count

Daily downloads

package

Tidyverse core package name
